Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:05.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:09.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:10.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:24.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:24.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:26.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:30.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:05.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you might have this bruise for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Kunisaki-kun, Kamio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:11.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:24.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It started when Kano was still a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:28.21,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:32.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the first summer after our mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, balloons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.56,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(289,251)\frz0.5\c&H0D2E6A&}BALLOONS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:45.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, if I bought one, would I be able to fly in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:53.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If one balloon could lift a person, the stall would have flown away by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:01.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then that means I can fly through the sky if I have lots of  balloons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:04.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, maybe then you could fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:10.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can only afford one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:15.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's one balloon, we'll just have to blow it up really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:19.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, it'll be able to lift much more weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we won't be able to buy anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:27.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank you, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kano always wanted to fly through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because she believed that she could see her mother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:45.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told her that her mother was in the sky, watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:49.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Neither Father nor I could tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that her mother was no longer around anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's playing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:59.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We put the feather back and went home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:13.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't go to where Mommy is anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The following morning, Kano started acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She became afraid of bright lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and she started wandering around outside in a daze,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,mumbling nonsense to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One night, Kano was gone before I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I rushed to look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:35.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found her in the examination room, pressing a scalpel to her wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught her in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I realized then; she wasn't Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like someone else was pretending to be Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a case of multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:51.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a magical bandana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:59.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep wearing it until you're an adult, you'll be able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:02.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, no matter what happens, never take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the one who gave Kano the bandana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:12.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she ever tried to unconsciously cut her wrist again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd see the bandana and come to her senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano doesn't really remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:24.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There never was any such thing as magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:28.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to follow in my father's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:32.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I became a doctor, I'd be able to cure Kano's illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that feather that Kano touched?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it's been there at the shrine for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the shrine-keeper doesn't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's the curse of that feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:51.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a doctor, I can't accept that kind of explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's possible that the feather was a psychological trigger for her illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:59.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Kano was suffering from a lot of stress after losing her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably the root cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to Kirishima-san's place today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go visit Kano later too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:12.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad you made a new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I had another dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream of flying through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:25.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this dream, I was traveling further and further back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:32.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I was mourning in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were mourning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:40.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, my body was soaring through the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:52.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why I felt so sad surrounded by such beautiful, comforting breezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not smiling, I also feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:36.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you picking up stuff like that to collect garbage or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Collecting interesting things from places like this is my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most pathetic hobby ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to play day in and day out. You're in a very enviable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty much like that too, aren't you, Yukito Kunisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:00.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'm on my way to my job right now to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that, by any chance, Tohno's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:20.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:38.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, call Minagi over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:42.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's lonely all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a walk with Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:25.10,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&HD5D5D5&\4c&H222222&\shad2\pos(421,172)}Sakuma Cycling Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:03.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:04.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:09.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you with Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:17.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Michiru say anything about the person who was with me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:25.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:30.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I once helped her with a big cart of groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the two of you are rather similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:38.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a fragment of that person's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:52.95,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko pikopiko piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll scrub you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko... Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yukito-kun. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It seems that I caused you troubled yesterday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came, Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of work for you to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kano-san taking a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to rest because of what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for her to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:46.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yukito-kun, I am writing this to you because I think you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:49.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally decided to go to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:53.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling that it will make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling that I will meet the girl you are looking for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know how long it will take,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I will definitely bring her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:05.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd be grateful if you could help Onee-chan until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know she is under a lot of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:13.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}P.S. I'm really sorry about the bruise on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.51,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Pikopikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.79,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopikopikopikopiko pikopikopikopikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.31,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko. Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.57,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko piko piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no superficial wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to be life-threatening,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but what on Earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she tried to go up to the sky from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:58.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:16.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, my emotions are acting up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like I'm nostalgic... or sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay Kano down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Shiraho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:51.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please listen to my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:57.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember – it was a beautiful autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:01.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My husband and I had our first child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:05.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She had a birthmark on her right wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:10.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The villagers said it was ominous, but we never paid them any attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:17.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Yakumo cried, I sang her a lullaby that I had learned from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:22.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yakumo would always stop crying, but that day, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:39.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that the feather was a charm sent by God for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:59.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A war started, and my husband, like many others, never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:11.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone in this village pick up a shining feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:16.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is cursed! Anyone who has touched it should step forward and confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That night, I fled from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I arrived at this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:47.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The chief priest of the shrine was very kind to us outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:55.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that Yakumo and I would be able to start a new life in this peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:16:03.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, that summer, an epidemic spread through the village, killing many.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Priest, how is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fever will come down in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:17.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the villagers believe the two of you brought the epidemic to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:24.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to invite the two of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We worship a divine idol here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:31.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The idol gives a sign to those who bring bad fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:37.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the villagers discover her birthmark, they will demand her to be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to sacrifice her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this land, we have always averted disasters by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:53.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only treasure my husband left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you will be killed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:25.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What mother would kill her own child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:29.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it might destroy the world, what mother could bear to kill her own child?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, somehow, save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:10.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm already full!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:24.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'll go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Potato too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:33.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And a new friend I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's looking for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:42.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of wish that I were that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If things are too hard for you, you can come with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember much about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:03.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I might have cut your life short,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:10.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving birth to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:11.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so live happily down there.
