Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san, you saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:43.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:55.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:59.90,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was that feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:17.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I met Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't go to where she was,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was able to thank her, just like Yukito-kun told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it soar into the sky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:43.48,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(300,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:46.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:53.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just get in the way, so I'm always playing by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:57.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:01.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother couldn't accept reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:05.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she chose to live in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:08.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:20.17,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,0)\fs39\fscx100\fscy100\shad2.4\c&HFEFEFA&\4c&H121213&\pos(314,419)}Episode 5
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.88,0:00:38.03,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}We watched the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.58,0:00:42.48,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}They were so dazzling, I ran away
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.49,0:00:51.86,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}I was so frustrated, I released your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.59,0:00:59.71,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}The place she can't reach is still there in the distance
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.47,0:01:06.79,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}She gazes at  it, keeping her wish to herself
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.10,0:01:15.24,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Children walk along the summer railway tracks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.47,0:01:21.80,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Holding in both hands their wishes to take flight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.00,0:01:29.09,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Chasing, chasing the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.96,0:01:36.74,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}It hasn't changed since the day we crossed that hill
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.00,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And never will
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.07,0:01:45.14,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And just as we are now, standing tall
